OL,3,CDundee to host Scottish album awards
OL,4,Cfor next three years
OL,6,FDundee will host the Scottish Album of
OL,7,Fthe Year (Say) Award ceremony for the
OL,8,Fnext three years, the award's
OL,9,Forganisers have announced.
OL,11,FThe city's Caird Hall will host this
OL,12,Fyear's ceremony on November 6 and then
OL,13,Fagain in 2026 and 2027, marking the
OL,14,Ffirst time it has been held outwith
OL,15,Fthe central belt in the award's 14-
OL,16,Fyear history.
