OL,3,CDundee to host Scottish album awards
OL,4,Cfor next three years
OL,6,FThe venue takes over the from
OL,7,FStirling's Albion Halls, which hosted
OL,8,Fthe event from 2022-2024, with the
OL,9,Fceremony moving to a different part of
OL,10,Fthe country every three years.
OL,12,FThe Scottish Music Industry
OL,13,FAssociation (SMIA), which runs the
OL,14,Faward, made the announcement a week
OL,15,Fbefore submissions for this year's
OL,16,Fprize open on July 1.
OL,18,FTo be eligible albums have to meet the
OL,19,FSay Award criteria, including being
OL,20,Freleased between June 1, 2024 and May
OL,21,F31, 2025.
