OL,6,FThis year's eligible artists include
OL,7,FPrimal Scream, Franz Ferdinand, Nina
OL,8,FNesbitt and Erland Cooper, among many
OL,9,Fothers.
OL,11,FPrevious winners of the award include
OL,12,FYoung Fathers, Mogwai, Fergus
OL,13,FMcCreadie and Auntie Flo.
