OL,3,CDundee to host Scottish album awards
OL,4,Cfor next three years
OL,6,FRobert Kilpatrick, chief executive and
OL,7,Fcreative director of SMIA said:
OL,8,F"Following three incredible years
OL,9,Fhosting Scotland's national music
OL,10,Fprize at Stirling's Albert Halls, the
OL,11,FSMIA is both delighted and proud to be
OL,12,Fcalling Dundee's iconic Caird Hall the
OL,13,Fnew home of the Say Award.
OL,15,F"Established in 2012 and originally
OL,16,Fhosted in Glasgow, we introduced our
OL,17,FHost City model in 2016 to broaden the
OL,18,FSay Award's reach, deepen place-based
OL,19,Fimpact and ensure nationwide cultural
OL,20,Fbenefit.
