OL,3,CDundee to host Scottish album awards
OL,4,Cfor next three years
OL,6,F"Since then, we've worked in three-
OL,7,Fyear cycles to move the ceremony
OL,8,Facross the country; supporting
OL,9,Fregional industry development,
OL,10,Festablishing local partnerships and
OL,11,Fcelebrating the strength and diversity
OL,12,Fof Scotland's ever-evolving recorded
OL,13,Foutput in a range of cultural contexts.
OL,15,FMr Kilpatrick said they had long
OL,16,Faspired to hold the ceremony in
OL,17,FDundee, and that now was the "perfect
OL,18,Ftime to do so".
