OL,6,F"Through our partnership with Leisure
OL,7,F& Culture Dundee, V&A Dundee, Dundee
OL,8,FCity Council and Unesco Dundee City of
OL,9,FDesign, we're excited to amplify the
OL,10,Fcity's creative identity and welcome
OL,11,Fover 1,500 guests from across
OL,12,FScotland, the wider UK and beyond to
OL,13,Four 2025 Ceremony on Thursday 6
OL,14,FNovember."
OL,16,FIn recognition of Dundee's status as a
OL,17,F"cultural powerhouse" ` and the UK's
OL,18,Ffirst and only Unesco City of Design `
OL,19,Fthe trophies for this year's awards
OL,20,Fare set to be created by a local
OL,21,FDundee designer.
