OL,3,CDundee to host Scottish album awards
OL,4,Cfor next three years
OL,6,FThe 2025 ceremony will feature a
OL,7,Fperformance by 2024 winner Redolent,
OL,8,Fand the winner of the Say will take
OL,9,Fhome #20,000 along with the coveted
OL,10,Faward, while nine runners-up will each
OL,11,Freceive #1,000.
OL,13,FAlongside the main prize the winner of
OL,14,Fthe Modern Scottish Classic Award will
OL,15,Fbe announced, recognising a cherished
OL,16,Falbum from Scotland's past that still
OL,17,Finspires Scottish musicians today.
