OL,3,CDundee to host Scottish album awards
OL,4,Cfor next three years
OL,6,F"Music of all kinds provides the
OL,7,Fsoundtrack to our city, whether it's
OL,8,Fthe vibrant busking culture we have in
OL,9,Fthe city centre, open-air gigs by
OL,10,Festablished acts at Slessor Gardens or
OL,11,Fup and coming grassroots bands in many
OL,12,Fof our small pubs and clubs," she said.
OL,14,F"We have always been a city with a
OL,15,Fpassion for music, and I am delighted
OL,16,Fthat the SMIA has chosen to make
OL,17,FDundee the home of the Say Award for
OL,18,Fthe next three years in a way that
OL,19,Frecognises this."
