OL,6,FAnna Day, head of libraries and
OL,7,Fculture at Leisure & Culture Dundee
OL,8,Fsaid she "couldn't be happier" the
OL,9,Faward was coming to Dundee.
OL,11,F"As the musical heart of the city for
OL,12,Fgenerations, Caird Hall is ready for a
OL,13,Fbold new chapter," she said.
OL,15,F"Partnering on the Say Award marks a
OL,16,Fmajor step in our broader ambition to
OL,17,Fre-energise what the Caird Hall offers
OL,18,Fto audiences, artists and partners. We
OL,19,Fnow can't wait to welcome the Scottish
OL,20,Fmusic community through its doors and
OL,21,Fonto its stage."
